            "text": "Dar on rūz voj ʙar durūƣʙarorandagon"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 77,
            "verse": 48,
            "text": "Va cun gūjandaşon, ki ruqū' kuned, ruqū' namekunand (namoz namexonand)"
